comment: Young (IND) maintains legal guarding position and Plumlee (POR) loses control of the ball.
Plumlee (POR) and Turner (IND) make incidental contact attempting to retrieve the loose ball.
Plumlee (POR) sets the screen on Teague (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Turner (IND) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
George (IND) and Plumlee (POR) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Lillard (POR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with George (IND) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Harkless (POR) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Plumlee (POR) makes contact with George (IND) that affects his SQBR.
Young (IND) and Harkless (POR) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
[Observable in enhanced video] Lillard (POR) moves his pivot foot.
LHH shows that Teague (IND) maintains legal guarding position during Lillard's (POR) shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Stuckey (IND).
Teague (IND) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) makes incidental contact with Stuckey (IND) that does not affect his SQBR.
